    dc:description "FIGURES 259–262. Phaeoxantha (Euphaeoxantha) testudinea (Klug.), ♂, LT, from Pará, Brazil (MFNB). 259—habitus, 25.3 mm; 260—labels; 261—head; 262—mandibles. Bar = 1 mm. Image credit Bernd Jaeger." ;
