<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10376690>
    dc:description "FIGURES 263–267. Phaeoxantha (Euphaeoxantha) testudinea (Klug.), (MFNB), from Pará Brazil. 263–265—♀, Rio Ara- guay: 263—habitus, 24.5 mm; 264—buccal appendages; 265–266—elytra: 265—♀, Rio Araguay; 266—♂, LT; 267—prono- tum, ♂, LT. Bars = 1 mm. Image credit Bernd Jaeger." ;
