<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10376692>
    dc:description "FIGURES 268–269. Phaeoxantha (Euphaeoxantha) testudinea (Klug.) from Mato Grosso, Brasil (RLHC). 268—habitus, ♂, 23.8 mm; 269–aedeagus (missing its basal portion). Bars = 1 mm. Image credit Mark Ryan." ;
